# GHM Backend Setup README

## Install Required Packages

### Main Dependencies

npm install express prisma @prisma/client swagger-ui-express swagger-jsdoc dotenv cors helmet morgan zod bcrypt jsonwebtoken multer cloudinary cookie-parser express-rate-limit compression


---

## Install Nodemon

npm install -D nodemon
```

---

# Prisma Commands

## Generate Prisma Client

npx prisma generate
```

---

## Run Migration

npx prisma migrate dev --name create_users_table



